WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.550 --> 00:00:04.870
Send me some freshly picked white truffles from Europe

2
00:00:04.870 --> 00:00:07.870
and mix them with some common mushrooms.

3
00:00:07.870 --> 00:00:10.869
Get me some fresh Mediterranean bluefish tuna

4
00:00:10.869 --> 00:00:13.509
but make it look like the cheap can stuff.

5
00:00:13.509 --> 00:00:17.750
I want my husband to do something nice, but I don't want to freak him out.

6
00:00:17.750 --> 00:00:34.289
Are you sure this is just common creamy tuna and mushroom pasta?

7
00:00:34.289 --> 00:00:36.090
It looks suspicious.

8
00:00:36.090 --> 00:00:37.689
Yeah, it's so normal.

9
00:00:37.689 --> 00:00:40.619
It's almost as it gets.

10
00:00:40.619 --> 00:00:45.210
Okay, I will leave you.

11
00:00:45.210 --> 00:00:50.590
You know, like the worst case scenario is just, we both get diarrhea.

12
00:00:50.590 --> 00:00:58.259
Can I ask you something?

13
00:00:58.259 --> 00:01:02.969
If you have such a good taste in food, why do you have such bad taste in men?

14
00:01:02.969 --> 00:01:05.129
How do you end up with that scumbag?

15
00:01:05.129 --> 00:01:11.109
Actually, I don't think I love him.

16
00:01:11.109 --> 00:01:13.909
I'm very grateful for him though.

17
00:01:13.909 --> 00:01:19.909
Three years ago on Halloween, I got in this really bad car accident and broke my life

18
00:01:20.909 --> 00:01:24.040
and he saved me when I woke up in the hospital.

19
00:01:24.040 --> 00:01:27.459
He was the first person I saw.

20
00:01:27.459 --> 00:01:28.459
Halloween.

